{"TopicId":154810,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"I need permission of copyright for my social project in Brazil","CreatedByName":"Felipe Lincoln","CreatedById":173351,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-11T00:48:19Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Felipe Lincoln","CreatedById":173351,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-11T00:48:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m working on a free book to give to libraries here in Brazil and I made a cover with a screenshot of the game. I already sent e-mail requesting but no answer. Someone can help me?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-11T03:18:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis looks like a question for \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-badie/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022149302\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/149302-badie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Badie\u003C/a\u003E, but she will need more information. What kind of book?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, moved to Kerbal Network.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Felipe Lincoln","CreatedById":173351,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-11T11:20:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for the reply, I\u0027ll send here the email I sent.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;font-size:12.8px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\nHi, I\u0027m Felipe, about to get admitted at USP (University of S\u00E3o Paulo) and my friend Miguel, already graduated at ITA (Aeronautics Institute of Technology).\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;font-size:12.8px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u00A0 \u00A0 \u00A0 \u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\nWe are working on a social project. We got a physics book, the book is already released but in PDF, it\u0027s completely free and the main porpose of this book is to help students to get admitted in the best universities in Brazil.\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;font-size:12.8px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\nSince we need to publish the book, we are working on a new layout to fit the properties of a book, because it\u0027s currently a simple article and doesn\u0027t have a cover.\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\nI played Kerbal Space Program and would love to use a single screenshot of the game on our cover. Because this show the reader everything about the content he will see, it fit to our purpose perfectly!\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;font-size:12.8px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\nOur goals isn\u0027t making money with this book, We\u0027ll freely share with as many\u00A0library here in Brazil as we can, with our money. So I\u0027m here requesting the Copyright to use the image in the\u00A0attachment.\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;font-size:12.8px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\nI\u0027m sending our current pdf version of the book, the cover we pretend to use, and the full image used in the cover.\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;font-size:12.8px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\nThe book is meant to be free and although it\u0027ll be on the libraries it\u0027ll also be in pdf in the internet.\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;font-size:12.8px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;font-size:12.8px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\nBest regards from me and Miguel.\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv style=\u0022color:rgb(34,34,34);font-family:arial, sans-serif;font-size:12.8px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);\u0022\u003E\nWe\u0027re anxiously waiting for the answer.\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll the attachment I uploaded on MEGA.\u003Cbr\u003E\nHere it is:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://mega.nz/#F!j842SZrC!Sxm6sH2F_EvF-3HA2coU0Q\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://mega.nz/#F!j842SZrC!Sxm6sH2F_EvF-3HA2coU0Q\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Darth Badie","CreatedById":149302,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-12T14:50:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi Felipe, we will get back to you with an answer by email \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Felipe Lincoln","CreatedById":173351,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-12T16:18:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks Badie. I already received a answer from\u00A0\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:rgb(0,0,0);font-family:arial, sans-serif;font-size:12.8px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;word-spacing:0px;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);float:none;\u0022\u003EAlejandro. Thank you anyway \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}